# info
http://www.discogs.com/release/2538491
Meilė Ir Mirtis Veronoje / Love and Death in Verona / Любовь и смерть в Вероне
Melodiya 1984 2LP C60-21309-005

A lithuanian musical / rock-opera written by KĘSTUTIS ANTANĖLIS (music) & SIGITAS GEDA (lyrics) with some worth tunes in it. I've made a slight re-edit of a song from there for certain project of mine some time ago but finally the work had no application, so here it go:

[verona edit 2.mp3] 

A question arises in my head about rock-operas: why do their authors always make their product worse than it could be? That theatrical, eccentric and non natural style of singing spoils all the party.

